Dialogs.Dialog: Oh, it looks like the battery is running low. Shall we charge it?
...No. Because... Geez, I don't know anymore.
Welcome back. You come back early?
Yes. Did you give your best today? Welcome!
Oh, wait. You forgot you good luck kiss... hmm, good luck.
▲主人公＊▲、welcome home. How was your day?
▲主人公＊▲、welcome home. Thank you for your hard work▼
▲主人公＊▲, welcome home. A welcome kiss▼ I'm kidding...
Fufu, bon appetit. Eat slowly, okay?
It looks delicious... Hmm▼ I'm kidding。
Which is delicious, my home cooking? ...I'm kidding.
Yes. Did you clean it? Fufu.
You shouldn't forget to brush your teeth, okay?
Yes. See you tomorrow? Good night.
Put me down? ...I'm kidding。Fufu~, good night.
Good night. Even in dreams, I wish we could meet... I'm kidding。
Hey, what are you interested in these days?
Fufu~, looks fun. Am I interested in it too?
I see. Hey, let's find something we can enjoy together, right?
That's right, can you tell me more about it?
Hey, what kind of music are you listening to lately?
There are times like that, right? You may understand.
Show me your favorite songs next time? Promise.
Are there any interesting TV shows these days?
I might be curious. Can you show me?
I see. If you find a program that looks fun, please let me know okay?
Do you want to see it together someday? I'm kidding。
Hey, what is my charm point?
...Nothing will come of it even if you praise me. Fufu!
That's good after all. Because, it's emarrassing...
Hey, do you like my hairstyle?
Emm... Well, maybe I should try a different hairstyle.
Tell me next time, okay? I want to be your favorite anytime. I'm kidding.
Hey, what about the clothes I'm wearing? Do you like them?
I'm glad to hear that. Fufu.
Yes... well, should we do more?
Will you coordinate it all next time? Fufu.
Hmm... I wonder if I should do something...
I see. Don't overstuff it, okay?
Is it okay because it doesn't disturb you? Fufu.
I haven't slept lately... Maybe it's your fault...
That's right. Geez... there's no changing it...
It doesn't make a difference... Geez, it's good now.
Thinking of you, I... I can sleep tonight, surely...
Me too. There were various things... Geez, don't look too much.
... You're so bad. Geez, I won't go with you anymore.
Hey, don't you think you're too close to me...?
Good. Then, I'm going to continue to mess with you, right? I'm kidding.
I don't want to leave... I want to be with you forever...
Hey, did you think of me now?
I knew it. It's my heart, isn't it? Fufu!
You make that face when you try to trick me, isn't it? Fufufu!
Am I full of you? Forever...
Hey, when do you think you're happy?
When I'm with you. I wish we could continue forever...
Fufu, it seems like you. I also like that... I'm kidding.
Hmm? I wonder about it. I'm just with you.
Hey, hey... I love you. I'm kidding。
Will you stay by my side?
I'm starting to get sleepy... hmm...
Isn't this kind of good? Fufu.
Hey, come here, close your eyes okay? Kiss! Were you surprised? Fufu~!
Hey, did you call me? Fufu, geez.
I want to eat sweets... Ah, it's a soliloquy, you don't mind? Right?
...Ah! Um... did you hear me? Oh, geez...
Hey, give me your hand, please? Fufu, it's warm.
I like the smell of spring...
Do you want to go to the park and have lunch?
The green is getting darker, right?
I want to eat ice cream▼
Autumn leaves, I want to go see it.
The day has ended, isn't it?
I want to eat some sweet potatoes.
Outside, your breath was white, right?
My hands are cold, so I want you to warm them... I'm kidding。
Perhaps you were awake all the time? Not getting enough sleep is bad, okay?
Good morning... is it early? Huh...
Ah... has it happened? I'm sorry?
Geez, you can sleep a little more, right?
Fufu~, are you asleep? Geez, it's past 7pm, right?
Good morning, did you sleep well?
Don't forget to check the weather forecast, okay?
Fufu, are you still sleepy? Hey, wake up?
What are your plans for today? I wish I could be with you...
Washing and cleaning? Fufu~, do you want to to it together?
I wonder what I should do for lunch today.
Is it lunch break? Let's eat together▼
I'm full... I ate too much.
I feel sleepy at this time...
Hey, should we take a break? I want to relax with you. Can I?
What do you want for dinner? I wonder if I can use it for future reference. Fufu.
Let's go for dinner shopping... together? I'm kidding。
Oh, I'm hungry... Can we have dinner early?
If we lived together, I could make it...
Now, let's get ready for dinner.
I want to eat dinner with you... I'm kidding.
Are there any interesting shows right now?
Are you watching the news at home?
Hey, have you taken a bath already?
Isn't it nice to have a relaxed atmosphere after dinner?
Be sure to brush your teeth before you go to bed, okay?
Hey, can I go sleep first?
Don't forget the door lock, okay?
I... I wonder if I'll be able to sleep like this...
It's amazing that you can wake up at such a time...
I was still awake... Yes, I was thinking of drinking some water...
It's past 1am, right? Well, shall we go to sleep now?
You stayed up late? It's not okay forgetting to sleep, okay?
Fufu, I knew it. I got up and woke you up.
If you don't sleep, you'll really oversleep?
Can't you sleep? Then, do you want to go out with me?
I woke up... Hey, can I stay with you?
Thank you for coming to see me many times. I'm so happy▼
You come to see me everyday... do you want to make me happy?
I'm looking forward to seeing you. I'm kidding。
Your time is mine. I'm kidding, fufu！
We've been together like this... Can we make more memories in the future?
Have you meet with other girls recently? It concerns me, but it's fine...
Wow, it's getting wide... Did you move?
My dream was that you could watch me like this... I'm glad. It's just a little bit, fight.
It's almost time to reach our goal, right? Thank you for your cooperation.
I said that's no good... No! Just because.
You can do many things today? I'm looking forward to it, okay?
Hey, did you try something new? I want to know how was it like.
Hey, did you try something new? I'm interested, so please let me know your impressions.
You haven't been meeting with me recently? Why?
Um... I wonder why you haven't kissed me...
I don't even know what to do...
I'm just crazy that I like it...
... It's a promise, okay? If you break it, it's no good...
If this is... Yes, it feels good.
I knew it, I should go over there...
And sent. The reply will come soon...
Is it time to check the horoscope?
It looks like something good will have happen today. Fufu！
...Good, I don't believe in bad things.
It looks like your luck is really good. Want me to tell you?
Dear, it looks like you will have a good day. Fufu.
Your luck is neither bad nor worse, maybe?
Your luck... is not very good.
Thank you for your hard work today...
I want to sleep like this...
I wonder if it's better to be thin...
How much do you like it?
Is this a little too cute?
You're okay, right? I can't show it...
What do you like? I can't hear... I'm kidding.
...I wonder if boys should be bigger...
Let's go visit the store next time.
... I wonder if we should do this a little more...
Phew. Let's leave a little later...
I want to wake up with your kiss, I'm kidding... Fufu.
I don't want to get out of the futon...
Even in dreams, I can meet you... Fufu.
It's just a little bit better...
Um, is that...? ...Ah, it was your home...
Was it fun? You were there... Fufu~.
Hey, let's do the countdown between us, okay?
Hey, let's do a lot of thing together, okay? Many more than last year.
Then, put what you want to choose separately on my right and left sides, okay?
Umm... I may understand how you feel.
Hmm... Which one should I do?
Hey, was it that good that I choose it?
I'm glad I could help you▼
If you'd like, you can always ask me, so please tell me okay?
What happened? If you'd like, ask me anything, okay?
Maybe there are times like that?
There will be good things. Right?
I want to see you in good spirits, okay?
Hey, did you laugh? Luck comes from the laughing corner!
Did you get tired from running? Shall we take a break?
Did you give your best? Let's do it together.
I'm always on your side, okay?
Do you feel a little better? ...If so, I'm glad.
Yes, that's about it. If something happens again, please tell me right away, okay?
Emm... So I'll sleep with you, right?
Will you be here until I sleep?
A good night rest. Fufu, aren't you spoiled?
Geez, I'm going to bed already...
Is it okay? Did you hear me?
Sorry, did I wake you up? It looked painful, but are you okay?
Good morning... I fell asleep... Ehe.
Do you want to stretch together? Okay.
Occasionally I'm wondering if I can do some excercise with you other than club activities.
I see. Then, call me again okay?
First, stretch your legs. Stretch your left hand on your waist and your right next to your ear, okay?
If I say 1, 2, 3, 4, then continue with 5, 6, 7, 8.
Emm, say it with a louder voice, okay?
Then you're going to the other side, right?
Reach your Achilles tendon. Bend your right leg and stretch the other back. And put your hands on your hips.
Last, open both legs and bend forward. Slowly touch your toes, the put your hands on your hips.
Yes, this ends stretching, okay? Let's do it again.
I want to move my body a little. How about doing it together?
Hey, can we do pushups together?
Yes, let's do our best okay?
Is that so? Be careful with the lack of exercise, okay?
A set of 10 push-ups. How many sets?
Yes, this might be all right to start with.
That's right, can I do this much?
Emm, it's a little difficult, but is it okay?
50 sets? Don't overdo it! Is that okay?
Really? If it's hard, you can stop it mid-way, okay?
Then, shall we start? I will count while you do it.
Are you sure you want to stop?
Thank you for your hard work. Did you sweat a lot?
Did you sweat? Should I wipe it for you? Fufu.
Isn't it good to move your body?
I wonder if I can try it... can you count?
Phew. It feels good to move your body. Fufu~.
... I have to work a little more...
Thank you for your hard work. Let's exercise together again, okay?
I'm sweating... I should take a shower.
Do you want to do abs?
One set is 10 abs, how many sets?
Oh, do you play games? I want to do it too.
Hey, can we play games together?
I see. Then, let's do it again next time okay?
I did it. Won't you lose today?
I did it. I'll take care of you today, okay? I'm kidding.
Is it okat? Aika will do her best! I'm kidding.
Will you quit? I see, next time then?
Hah~, it was fun! Hey, do you want to try again?
I did it. Then, shall we do it from the beginning?
Hmm, I understand. We had fun, right?
Thank you for your hard work. Let's play together next time, okay?
Somehow, it looks you're in pain...
Can I go for a little longer?
I don't know what to say at times like this, I don't know I can say it well... Want to hear?
When you feel sad, you feel like you're alone, right? I understand that...
I used to do that sometimes, but...
But, I'm okay because you're here.
When you're sad, I'm sure you're thinking about me somewhere.
Then, I will be able to do my best.
Even if you don't like it, I can be gentle when I think about you.
Even in a dark night, when I remember your voice, it gets warm. I will be strong because you're there.
Hey... I might not be like that... but I...
I want to be that kind of person for you too. I want to be a girl you can remember when you feel lost.
Aika is here. Wherever you are, Aika always thinks of you.
If you're sad and you think all is lost, just think of me.
Please call me anytime and talk to me. I want to whatever I can.
